Package: wedge
Type: Package
Title: The Exterior Calculus
Version: 1.0-3
Depends: spray (>= 1.0-7)
Suggests: knitr, Deriv, testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports: permutations (>= 1.0-4), partitions, magrittr, methods
Authors@R: person(
	   given=c("Robin", "K. S."),
	   family="Hankin",
	   role = c("aut","cre"),
